  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/Network\/nw_service_class_background\ncrawled: 2025-12-11T23:39:02Z\n---\n\n# nw_service_class_background\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nBulk traffic, or traffic that can be deprioritized behind foreground traffic.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar nw_service_class_background: nw_service_class_t { get }\n```\n\n## Service classes\n\n- **nw_service_class_best_effort**: Default priority traffic.\n- **nw_service_class_interactive_video**: Interactive video traffic.\n- **nw_service_class_interactive_voice**: Interactive voice traffic.\n- **nw_service_class_responsive_data**: Responsive user-data traffic.\n- **nw_service_class_signaling**: Signaling control traffic.\n\n",
